subtemplate.unicode: [[b]]Investigate Issues[[/b]] \n This will show you outstanding issues in your realm.
Known Factions ||A list of all the factions you have encountered so far. Double left-click a faction to travel to its capital, or right-click a faction to initiate Diplomacy.
Commanderies ||A list of all commanderies and their attached counties that you own. Double left-click a commandery or county to move the camera to its location.
Armies ||A list of all the armies in your faction. Double left-click an army to move the camera to its location.
Characters ||A list of all the characters in your faction. Double left-click a character to move the camera to their location, or right-click them to open their character details panel.
Missions ||A list of all your missions and objectives. Left-click a mission to see more details.
Pins ||Highlight commanderies, cities and other elements relevant to your campaign. Create your own custom pins to track and immediately jump to specific points on the campaign map.
